<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Basket" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Basket,</orth> a vessel made of twigs or other things interwoven: <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 3, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 3, 13</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 3, 13</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.5" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.5" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 5</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.5" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 5</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.33" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.33" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 33</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.33" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 33</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.193" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 193</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.193" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 193</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.343" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 343</bibl>. <cit><quote>Youth in a b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.122" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 2, 122</bibl></cit>, perhaps a proverbial expression, whose sense has not yet been ascertained.
